Class AFC

public class AFC
extends Object

This model software representation was created based on the model developed by Marca A. et al, 2011 This class facilitates the calculation of the AFC results based on the statistical model by Marca A. et al 2011 Article can be accessed at: http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0015028210021953
